{
  "message": "feat(dashboard): add VM detail page template\n\nAdds a comprehensive VM detail view with:\n- Header showing VM ID, status badge, Copy SSH button, and actions dropdown\n- Resources panel (placeholder with CPU/Memory/Network/Disk)\n- Logs panel (placeholder for Phase 2)\n- Details panel showing ID, Repository, Git Ref, Tailscale Host\n- Snapshots panel with table and empty state\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
